videos.description: Josh Anderson pounds in a 1-yard touchdown to give the Trojans an early lead.
videos.headline: Anderson punches in Troy TD

videos.description: Jamal Stadom sacks North Texas' Mason Fine, causing a fumble and a recovery for the Trojans.
videos.headline: Troy's Stadom gets a strip-sack

videos.description: Josh Anderson scores his second touchdown of the game with a 2-yard run.
videos.headline: Troy's Anderson gets his 2nd TD

videos.description: Rico Bussey Jr. makes a great adjustment to the ball and reels in a 33-yard reception along the sideline.
videos.headline: North Texas' Bussey makes great catch along sideline

videos.description: Mason Fine throws 12-yard touchdown pass to Rico Bussey Jr. for North Texas' first score of the game.
videos.headline: Bussey puts North Texas on the board

videos.description: Brandon Silvers throws a 7-yard touchdown pass to Damion Willis as Troy builds its lead vs. North Texas.
videos.headline: Willis snags pass for Troy TD

videos.description: Colton McDonald picks up Troy's bad snap and takes it 56 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Bad snap leads to North Texas TD

videos.description: Kishawn McClain jumps in front of the Brandon Silvers deep pass and comes down with an interception.
videos.headline: North Texas' McClain makes impressive INT

videos.description: Mason Fine lobs a pass to Michael Lawrence who dives to bring in a 13-yard touchdown for North Texas.
videos.headline: Lawrence makes diving TD grab

videos.description: Troy head coach Neal Brown says the team made errors in the first half that allowed North Texas to get back into the game.
videos.headline: Coach says Troy hurt itself in first half

videos.description: Mason Fine's pass is tipped in the air and then intercepted by Hunter Reese.
videos.headline: Troy's Reese gets tip drill INT

videos.description: Brandon Silver fights his way in for a 2-yard touchdown to give Troy a 29-20 lead over North Texas.
videos.headline: Silvers extends Troy's lead with rushing TD

videos.description: Troy's Brandon Silvers connects with Tevaris McCormick for a 59-yard Troy touchdown.
videos.headline: Silvers throws 59-yard TD

videos.description: The Trojans recover a Mason Fine fumble when he gets blindsided by an unblocked Tyler Murray.
videos.headline: Troy's Murray destroys Fine, gets strip-sack

videos.description: Some lights go out in the Superdome after Troy's John Johnson takes a screen pass for a 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Johnson's TD turns the lights out
